headline.main: LATER FROM HAVANA.; Arrival of the Black Warrior. New Financial Law--Dinner to Com. Spaulding--Mlio. Ruchel.

docs.lead_paragraph: The United States Mail steamer Black Warrior, J. W. SMITH, Commander, from New-Orleans the 25th and Havana the evening of the 28th, has arrived at this port. The United States frigate Potomac, Commodore ??, and war-steamer Fulton left for Key West the morning of the 28th. During their stay the officers dined at the Palace.

docs.lead_paragraph: The Theatres this week offer greater attractions than they have put forth for sometime, and we hope there will be a commensurate increase of business. It can no longer be disguised that the season so far has been unprofitable. Many causes can be assigned for this, not the least among which is the unusual severity of the weather, and especially the impassible state of the thoroughfares.

docs.lead_paragraph: The Board of Health of Norfolk are taking measures to preserve the future health of the city. They have adopted a report recommending to the City Councils, as of the first necessity, the draining of the lots on the north side of Water-street, on the south side of Cove-street, and on the east side of Metcalf's-lane, by culverts.

headline.main: ONE WEEK LATER FROM EUROPE; ARRIVAL OF THE ARABIA AT HALIFAX. NEWS HIGHLY IMPORTANT. Threat of the Austrian Embassy to Withdraw from St. Petersburg. Agreement of Russia to Negotiate on the Terms Proposed by the Allies.. Rise in the Funds and Cotton--Excitement in the other Markets. NOTHING IMPORTANT FROM THE CRIMEA. The Russians Advancing in Asia. WARLIKE PREPARATIONS BY SWEDEN, Favorable Opinions on the President's Message. BREADSTUFFS AND PROVISIONS DOWN. COTTON A FARTHING HIGHER. Consols 89 1-2a89 3-4. [By the House Printing Telegraph--Office 21 Wall-St.]

docs.lead_paragraph: The R. M. steamship Arabia, from Liverpool on the morning of Saturday, the 19th inst., with 107 passengers, arrived here at 9 1/9 o'clock this P.M. The Cunard steamship Asia arrived at Liverpool early on Sunday morning, the 13th inst., but lay off several hours for want of water.
